reviewText: I was in the movie too and made it quite a few times on screen. Would love to get a copy of the movie but so far have only found it as Austrailian  DVD. Cannot play in USA players. Are there any USA copies out there?  Had alot of fun as an extra on the movie.
I was in this movie when it was made but most have ended up on the cutting room floor lol. Movie was just ok even if I was not cut out it would still have been just ok.
